	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I know there are not many fighting games for the NES, mostly because of the sprite limitation I'd guess. But there are a few that I'm aware of:
<br />- Joy Mecha Fight (I really like this one!);
<br />- Datach Dragonball Z;
<br />- Datach Yuu Yuu Hakusho;
<br />- Some Ninja Turtles game;
<br />
<br />Does anyone know of any others? BTW, I'm not counting the endless pirate ones (Mortal Kombats, Street Fighters, Tekkens, etc), as they are badly programmed and barelly resemble an actual game.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
