		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />"Really bad" but Kart Fighter is better than Street Fighter 1, right?
<br />
<br />The Ninja Turtles game you refer to is <em>Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles Tournament Fighters</em>, and like <em>Kart Fighter</em>, it was plagued by flicker.
<br />
<br />I'm guessing that flicker can be mostly avoided in a homebrew fighting game by making each character roughly 32x64 pixels with 8x16 pixel sprites.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
